{"title":"Infección Sitio Operstorio (ISO)","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Infección Sitio Operstorio (ISO)-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Infección Sitio Operstorio\\N(ISO)","guid":"LGkeD3fEllZoCy0iEkCNGA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"ISO: General","guid":"rqUYs5q31W5pSpKgIQtZwg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Frecuencia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• +Fcte en pacientes hospitalizados, especialmente\\Nen países de ingresos bajos/medios (1).","guid":"e8HpgDaQ-WVpx4h0yuk4Ag","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• +Común en pacientes quirúrgicos (15%, varía según cirugía) (2).","guid":"rlgZiXwi8CuOITO8-YQBAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"• Impacto:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Alta morbi-mortalidad, ↑días de hospitalización y costos.","guid":"pL-a9GA5oiX1aVGpKfH7KA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Mayor riesgo en px mayores o con patologías crónicas.","guid":"9gB11GTuIa05cijE_7hEJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"• Definición (entre 1-30\\Ndías post-cirugía) (3):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"1. Pus por drenaje espontáneo o apertura de herida.","guid":"ia2MjO4572BcgLLpRUHfsA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"2. Fiebre, sensibilidad/dolor en incisión, aumento de volumen, eritema/calor local (≥2).","guid":"ikL4Bvk5iFmclbI6-ZX_Qw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"3. Cultivo positivo de agente obtenido con técnica aséptica desde superficie o tejido subcutáneo.","guid":"bD_LNCuIuy533e8vErv4EA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"Impacto ISO:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• Con ISO:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Mortalidad: 7.8%","guid":"gacHuGSEzESygAkyhtqfgA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• Admisión UPC: 29%","guid":"m_OfavDtc0NwAS56NkorOA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"• Re-hospitalización: 41%","guid":"eMaKWUrANsMFqHK7WHJ8NA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"• Días de hospitalización: 18 días","guid":"4p67OjDvJwDdNyZfaF2R5w","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"13","text":"• Costo adicional: US$ 5, 038 (mediana) (4).","guid":"INUALiDA7XyaTDOowXwbqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"12","text":"• Sin ISO:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Mortalidad: 3.5%","guid":"mY0XaA2JzDwz94XVSa_gFQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Etiología:","guid":"Lvt_RfQb9wWy0J9nl4LlWw","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Puede afectar tejido superficial, profundo, o un órgano/espacio intervenido en cirugía.","guid":"2sJnjx5PC_i-ke4K991BAQ","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• Depende del tipo de cirugía: agentes exógenos y endógenos → MO multirresistentes, eventos adversos ATB, etc.","guid":"-59t5ToYbSNGXnNr0jTsjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"Incidencia acumulada de ISO según\\Nprocedimiento quirúrgico (2008-2011)","guid":"62Ic4GBTBDT60pEUpMBckw","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• Cirugía de\\Nbypass coronario:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Incidencia: 3-5%","guid":"QEmz4dTHVVgmv5qzjccG2Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"• Colecistectomía:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Incidencia: <2%","guid":"beUEBQC4cOUL3ijw9Pb37w","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"• Cirugía de colon:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Incidencia: 9-10%","guid":"T6sMo7NEIajTysvyxhNp2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"24","text":"• Cesárea:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Incidencia: 5-6%","guid":"m7vkqpG10hs1UY72JVIBhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"24","text":"• Prótesis de cadera:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Incidencia: 2-3%","guid":"9gL6xj1Jsz6oV0JTh0rg_A","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"24","text":"• Prótesis de rodilla:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Incidencia: 1-2%","guid":"f8XAo1GYWv-sVhQx6Ro6sQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"24","text":"• Laminectomía:","guid":"r2wGIw2NUVkWt7z6e8wRiA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Incidencia: 1-2%","guid":"2xV00VniOoXJWtbKlZjAeQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Etiología según\\Ntipo de cirugía:","guid":"Z9sTfa0cZm1tRq8ratQckg","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Procedimientos: Implante/protésis, Cardiaca, Neurocirugía,\\NMama, Oftálmica, Ortopédica, No cardiotorácica, Vascular.","guid":"dsx-elCq7JsZA4m5q1F6yg","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• S. aureus","guid":"MkkQYJDMep1ebnSC-K8hKg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"• CoNS (S. epidermidis)","guid":"3uYay3VGjEZ3pqI_7izUaw","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"• Estreptococos","guid":"ZlKrswKOkNRBU5evsGPnzg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"40","text":"• Bacilos Gram-.","guid":"C9UpRXq-fekIe6Syy6lKyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"39","text":"• Procedimientos: Apendicectomía, Tracto biliar,\\NColorectal, Gastroduodenal, Cabeza y cuello,\\NObstétrica/ginecológica, Urológica.","guid":"Tz5rjKM5aiHdvHQjlbdMxA","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• Bacilos Gram-","guid":"4tZP9z_HMHKEyKM5Aoq21g","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"• Anaerobios","guid":"FdVUvCmKvhV1fppmO4-yJw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"• Enterococci","guid":"8xTNbc5Pe5aVEy4M_0N9Ew","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"• Streptococcus pneumoniae","guid":"IT16BLL6A_Entz5Ows91Sg","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"45","text":"• Orofaringeal anaerobios (peptostreptococci).","guid":"H-bjKCz7SaPHeW5jlSp5jQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"0","text":"ISO: Factores\\Nde Riesgo","guid":"V6lv5hNEr161WYasVAcmww","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Factores\\Ndel Paciente:","guid":"uOVXYfiEuEGp6R8Vsy6nFQ","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Preparación quirúrgica","guid":"fv5rVHprcnqgq_8LUdsbgw","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• Daño tisular","guid":"b50fbK8WdMP7fedYiPMmeQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"• Ambiente, CE, etc.","guid":"zhCmOl0cDto0QygNMnYr0w","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"• Antibióticos pre-operatorios.","guid":"xeJ9HGtMzCjDwMeb0eywqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"51","text":"• Factores\\NIntra-operatorios:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Pérdida de sangre","guid":"XiVdwvw9NYnmCjbeq1If1Q","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Temperatura","guid":"hhTbutxeuHpTaO19WJMbpQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• Glicemia","guid":"KcgN__xyFitRY3rJzuCRag","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"• Oxígeno.","guid":"jhsrjUYaOONFNFzXJRGHOQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"0","text":"Riesgo de Infección según Tipo\\Nde Herida Quirúrgica","guid":"d_-PGMFC0ph7XlQZQdWkCA","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"• Limpia: 1-3%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"• Limpia-contaminada: 5-8%","guid":"WIRKKK3q2M2jFL0OHnX0kQ","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"• Contaminada: 20-25%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"• Sucia: 30-40%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"0","text":"Guías de\\NPrevención de\\NISO","guid":"uATwWTdXwQ--haiTwgekoQ","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• WHO 2016: Estado\\Ndel conocimiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Ausencia de directrices internacionales unificadas.","guid":"Jugpo4TonQWj7NVRMAjZtw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"• Interpretación diversa de la evidencia disponible.","guid":"HIDhtUCCZ4k2EQBWhYHLQA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"• Recomendaciones locales no uniformes.","guid":"GY6Ox4SWjFCgqZkVMSQPUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"• Medidas de prevención\\Npropuestas:","guid":"ulPrnG9FqYfhOyMvxl8kZQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"• Válidas y adaptables a diferentes contextos.","guid":"jll2yyMCHw0KRexcQMfUeQ","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"• Uso de recursos más disponibles.","guid":"-aOIcGuoeJTgtRDelSqiUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"67","text":"• Consideración\\Nde:","guid":"j3GBXwbRyth0LioPEjD-BA","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"• Evidencia científica.","guid":"wft_8EswrYyVuN0IDV4ILQ","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"• Costos y recursos necesarios.","guid":"j3e0HSN2ljgsu21akoiNOQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• Valores y preferencias de los pacientes.","guid":"KZH5GpnMfLyRNs7Mm2FxJQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"67","text":"Medidas\\NPre-Operatorias","guid":"i55o1nWE51nv8n5OhZmHAQ","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Descolonización\\Ncon Mupirocina:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Prevención de infección por S. aureus en portadores nasales.","guid":"dsPBs9gPsqttcZqSTZsxAA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"• Mupirocina 2% (cada 12 h por 5-7 días), con o sin baños CHX.","guid":"0mj4jgziopG8daPZ2UAfDA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"• Indicada en cirugía TMT o cardiotorácica.","guid":"uDQyL6Sk0my2wSVElWPufA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"• Otras cirugías según prevalencia de S. aureus, colonización o infección previa conocida.","guid":"958qOkx7ovNMTOI0G4NRdw","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"80","text":"• Evaluación local de la necesidad de screening.","guid":"O0ExgV6tb_dWh996N8CW4g","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"80","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Fuerte","guid":"KXvYL6Gvp55hjQbpQCtOGw","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"80","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Moderada","guid":"Dbc6UIO9QqXLA3KODlwQVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"79","text":"• Oportunidad de\\NProfilaxis Antibiótica:","guid":"YshKU6XYJKJ-DXMcwmiN0A","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• Prevención antes de la incisión quirúrgica según tipo de cirugía (IB).","guid":"enB1P3YIGdaW_fHCO7xbjw","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"• Administración dentro de los 120 minutos previos a la incisión.","guid":"lChNb1MoX40kzzbylon1Bg","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"• Administración de profilaxis antibiótica pre-incisión de piel en cesárea (IA).","guid":"kXElQaTq8iLzFYe09YNmxg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"88","text":"• Considerar la vida media del antibiótico.","guid":"OsWXEkf1JUdWhaniZIqp7A","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"88","text":"• Sin precisión sobre indicación según duración de la cirugía, dosis de refuerzo, necesidad de infusión, etc.","guid":"6HnQSutn7PnSJtcTSF94Yw","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"88","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Fuerte","guid":"ycZfs--gWyX36-k7DlEvOw","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"88","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Baja","guid":"z3d7CT4lJYWqFeGt_IFxeA","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"79","text":"• Baño Pre-Operatorio\\Nprevio a la Cirugía:","guid":"fzCHjqflijmntkcoLd4H0Q","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Jabón simple o antiséptico* (IB).","guid":"MRtImVWcZtnhX9wf8KbKAA","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• Soluciones de clorhexidina (CHX) (generalmente 4%).","guid":"P-NTN-ovxi_J0gmY4uEK0w","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"• Jabón antiséptico en cirugías específicas → Artroplastía de cadera y rodilla.","guid":"d5tN-dLARSPFw_DdQJwHTw","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"• Extrapolable a pacientes pediátricos.","guid":"O3YWJtzzCGTqG0HMuVubaw","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"96","text":"• Toallas impregnadas con CHX → Información limitada.","guid":"ZyCJ61OC8vKmK0GXgx-6Tg","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"96","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Condicional","guid":"oJNkTM3aalrHvlOAettTzw","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"96","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Moderada","guid":"00dVblZEJLNiGuqNRhBfCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"79","text":"• Remoción\\Ndel Vello:","guid":"0MT7NFn0hJLPGUQQvfc_Xg","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"• No se recomienda eliminar el vello a menos que sea necesario.","guid":"lpgmqXs3WHGlbii8YCpatA","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"• Si es necesario, utilizar cortadora tipo clipper, no rasuradora.","guid":"-bY-R3LJoA0f8qvTWiYIQQ","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Fuerte","guid":"eSLyFDZrCbR_tJfamb--9A","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"104","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Moderada","guid":"TTro8PoGACafTu3HgiiYVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"79","text":"• Preparación del\\NSitio Quirúrgico:","guid":"cQChkGu5UWzmR34b7yNTbQ","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"• Uso de antisépticos basados en CHX alcohólica (IA).","guid":"n1L2vQp3WGA3zil5xu3ggw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"• Sin recomendación respecto a una concentración concreta.","guid":"cZ2ihejOuXfQh-Je3LfOXg","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"• Lavado de la piel fuera de Pabellón.","guid":"UoVMkiPAR15Hr4dtFaGnXQ","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"109","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Fuerte","guid":"uoplpmRDpZVdzSG5jTzkbw","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"109","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Baja a Moderada","guid":"oEtkC-LzOKuZqmH2AljSzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"79","text":"• Preparación del intestino con uso de antibióticos orales para cirugía colorrectal\\N(más profilaxis antibiótica endovenosa estándar).","guid":"80ZSAWr6kzrf_xdTRA3UEw","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Condicional","guid":"j9GB6tiUCyUueejLvSGRWw","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Moderada","guid":"ziaSb6cnmfRGlBUmq3VdAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"79","text":"• Lavado previo de manos\\Nfuera del área de Pabellón.","guid":"aXFBLz1F_8iJhLtEqsXrLw","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Uso de jabón antiséptico o solución hidroalcohólica con efectividad sostenida, por ejemplo, CHX.","guid":"mWDiUrirdEGuTmEJ4IxQmQ","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Fuerte","guid":"lZLwBNaVmW3VwSwxmYV3iw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"67","text":"Guías de\\NPrevención de\\NISO","guid":"GT_lxELcgETchbuE_SbWVA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"67","text":"Medidas Pre e\\NIntra-Operatorias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"• Anestesia\\NGeneral (c/ TOT):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"• Uso de FiO2 al 80%, mantener\\Ndurante cirugía y hasta 2-6 horas\\Nen postoperatorio (IA).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"• Grado de\\NRecomendación:\\NFuerte","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"122","text":"• Calidad de\\NEvidencia:\\NModerada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"122","text":"• Normotermia:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"122","text":"• Mantener normotermia con uso de\\Ndispositivos de calentamiento.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"122","text":"• Manejo de Glicemias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"122","text":"• Usar protocolos para manejo en\\Npacientes diabéticos y no diabéticos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"122","text":"• Mantener glicemias\\N<200 mg/dl (IA, CDC).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"122","text":"• Normovolemia:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"122","text":"• Mantener con terapia de\\Nfluidos guiada por metas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"122","text":"• Soporte Nutricional:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"122","text":"• Oral/Enteral en pacientes de\\Nbajo peso y cirugía mayor.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"122","text":"• Inmunosupresores:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"122","text":"• No suspender\\Nmedicamentos\\Ninmunosupresores.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"122","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia:\\NMuy baja o baja.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"67","text":"Medidas\\NIntra-Operatorias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"• Uso de batas y campos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Desechables o tejidos reutilizables estériles.","guid":"XP_rkgO9ptindgacMN4_NQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"• Dispositivos protectores de heridas:","guid":"Z2F2IuWBrJUieg49sOLFxg","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• En heridas quirúrgicas (limpia-contaminadas, contaminadas o sucias).","guid":"POzPg_bPFns8jcbP2Bh-cg","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"139","text":"• Irrigación de herida:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Sin recomendación de irrigación (S.F.) antes del cierre.","guid":"iGybL06rIL5NRwmMQUZcvA","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"139","text":"• Terapia de presión negativa:","guid":"sHj4jRu6THR3Fpkjg-FgIw","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"• Uso según recursos.","guid":"hcMZYFxPGWoOH5zvGKDHZg","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Condicional.","guid":"2F1Emql2OCOmWmhUIoRBJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"139","text":"• Guantes e instrumental quirúrgico:","guid":"uMav1nISGDvu95-bNgFA7g","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"• Sin evidencia de cambio de guantes (o doble guante) o instrumental quirúrgico.","guid":"PifC6_AGbXKyaSKR67iVXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"139","text":"• Sistemas de ventilación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Flujo laminar en cirugía de artroplastía.","guid":"AEVT4g4NuizVgnVkmN2tLA","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Muy baja a baja.","guid":"nHu1rIprjsZ53VPRBv1ylg","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"139","text":"• Suturas con triclosán:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"• Uso en diferentes tipos de cirugía (II).","guid":"2g7Z_1wZjIr3MCJYlIMLPA","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Moderada.","guid":"erVHGT_OLJUl8c4mw5OcLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"157","parent":"139","text":"• Implantes con soluciones\\Nantimicrobianos:","guid":"hBgsqee2gvLeHrtZ446Rpg","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"• Sin recomendación sobre su uso para heridas quirúrgicas,\\Nungüentos o polvos.","guid":"x6bGILdPBmLVhMm8e1cr1w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"67","text":"Medidas\\NPost-Operatorias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Profilaxis Antibiótica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• No prolongar la profilaxis antibiótica post-cirugía.","guid":"WCWLyWFxp-gCojmkn8HVCQ","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Fuerte","guid":"pSH9Js3Y8n1luDu8TZQDTg","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Moderada","guid":"3tiX09nCa3sfqDy61edoQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"159","text":"• Drenajes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"• Retiro según indicación clínica.","guid":"D9u-SPpz1HRwBCDyy-q6_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"159","text":"• Apósitos para\\Ncuraciones:","guid":"du9O_VQW30CjOlJkiLJW1A","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"• Sin necesidad de apósitos avanzados.","guid":"iaVwM0oykWYYV5dKLNs0oQ","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"• Grado de Recomendación: Condicional","guid":"EVH1koGtVDOBZxywy8EyBQ","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"• Calidad de Evidencia: Baja.","guid":"JdNhCJEwB3XQVm56M5FchA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"0","text":"Medidas Ambientales para\\Nla Prevención de ISO","guid":"uvoWclIox8MSbXIGOvx6Lw","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"Limpieza y\\NDesinfección","guid":"vHE0DGB17YE_Ayfb5twAow","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"• Limpieza:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• Paso imprescindible previo a la desinfección.","guid":"TrT4kU-YFeW0HwDO-WGrYg","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"• Previene formación de biofilm.","guid":"AFIBZ9AxSWdNL4gswfBqbA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"• Procedimiento: Desde zonas más limpias hacia las más sucias\\N(arriba → abajo).","guid":"9H2we07I6oX4o7WTlX1m7g","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"172","text":"• Evitar dispersión o aerosolización de contaminantes.","guid":"CTt1RbOHnXvTk9OlfmsStg","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"171","text":"• Superficies:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"• Desinfección enfocada en aquellas con contacto manual frecuente.","guid":"lBN_xv4xDdSm9jTNENdggA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"• Manejar inmediatamente superficies\\Ncontaminadas con sangre o fluidos corporales.","guid":"5Rz9XlZZMFxjSKhesB3Ngg","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"171","text":"• Desinfectantes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"• Usar dilución acorde a las recomendaciones del fabricante.","guid":"uRG9h2DMb43-QAL8XbNrZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"171","text":"• Evitar concentraciones bajas (menor\\Neficacia) o altas (daño a materiales).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"171","text":"• Eliminar soluciones\\Nposterior a cada uso.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"170","text":"Equipos de Protección y\\NProcedimientos","guid":"6rTOq1gXZmJgmB_qA2hygA","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• Equipos de protección:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"• Uso de guantes adecuados\\Ndurante el aseo y desinfección.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"• En algunas ocasiones: delantal,\\Nmascarillas, gafas, protección facial, etc.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"• Aseo y\\Nlimpieza\\Nprofunda:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"184","text":"• Realizar al final del día, no\\Nnecesariamente después de cada\\Nintervención (aunque sea cirugía\\Ncontaminada).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"184","text":"•\\NReprocesamiento\\Nde equipos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"184","text":"• Todos los equipos deben\\Nser reprocesados.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"184","text":"• Instrumental quirúrgico debe ser\\Ndesinfectado o esterilizado según la\\Nclasificación de Spaulding.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"184","text":"• Monitorización\\Nbacteriológica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"184","text":"• Eficacia de la higiene ambiental se\\Nmonitorea en casos de brotes o para fines\\Nde investigación o formación.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"0","text":"Conclusiones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"• ISO:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"• Siguen siendo frecuentes y de\\Ngran impacto en IAAS.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"195","text":"• Asociadas a importante\\Nmorbimortalidad y costos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"195","text":"• Factores influyentes:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"195","text":"• Diversos factores\\Ninfluyen en su desarrollo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"195","text":"• Énfasis en factores relacionados\\Ncon la atención de salud.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"195","text":"• Nuevas\\NRecomendaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"195","text":"• Estándares en prácticas pre, intra, y\\Npost-operatorias para prevención de ISO\\N(Norma Técnica 190, MINSAL 2017).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"195","text":"• Implementación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"195","text":"• Existe una brecha entre la evidencia y la\\Nimplementación de estas medidas, que\\Naún debe ser abordada.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":205,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Infección Sitio Operstorio (ISO)-2024-1","id":"map_1147","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Infección Sitio Operstorio (ISO)-2024-1"}